# Adding New Colors

To add new colors to the system:

1. **Add base color to `:root` section:**
```css
:root {
  /* Your new color */
  --u-your-color: #HEX_VALUE;
  --u-your-color-50: rgba(R, G, B, 0.50); /* Add opacity variants if needed */
}
```

2. **Create semantic alias (optional):**
```css
:root {
  --your-semantic-name: var(--u-your-color);
}
```

3. **Add theme-specific values for each mode:**
```css
/* Light Mode */
:root, [data-theme="light"] {
  --your-usage: var(--u-your-color);
}

/* Dark Mode */
[data-theme="dark"] {
  --your-usage: var(--u-your-color-modified);
}

/* Repeat for other theme modes... */
```

4. **Use in components:**
```css
.your-component {
  color: var(--your-usage);
  background-color: var(--your-usage);
}
```
